  - id: bastion
    displayName: Bastion
    role: Shield Vanguard
    description: The immovable wall. Bastion soaks up punishment on the front line
      and grinds enemies down with frost-touched shield strikes.
    portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: ca632839309545c41babece6fc06b439, type: 3}
